WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.609 --> 00:00:03.120
The nurse manager goes to the CPRC

2
00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:07.424
and requests the item to be added to area for patient care.

3
00:00:07.424 --> 00:00:09.859
The CPRC approves the item.

4
00:00:09.859 --> 00:00:11.761
It is determined that it can be purchased

5
00:00:11.761 --> 00:00:14.977
from the Prime Vendor, and the chief supply chain officer

6
00:00:14.977 --> 00:00:18.692
or logistics chief alerts the responsible IM.

7
00:00:18.692 --> 00:00:21.360
The responsible IM then executes the order

8
00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:24.221
and creates a purchase order in VistA.

9
00:00:24.221 --> 00:00:27.899
Since the order is under $3,500, it can be ordered

10
00:00:27.899 --> 00:00:30.643
using the government purchase card.

11
00:00:30.643 --> 00:00:34.791
IM determines that a level of 10 will be tentatively set

12
00:00:34.791 --> 00:00:38.121
for the area and creates a space in primary and secondary

13
00:00:38.121 --> 00:00:39.837
to store the clippers.

